    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-200 text-sm md:text-base">Sagri is an Asia-focused AgTech Startup, helping farmers live a happier life. We help farmers with easy-to-access credit and educate them in increasing their earning potential. We leverage satellite imagery and our proprietory soil sampling technology.</p>
